=<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email from Jack</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #2c3e50;
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 40px;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            color: #34495e;
        }

        .main-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .date {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 3px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #495057;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .gift-highlight {
            background: #e8f5e8;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }

        .gift-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #155724;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .signature {
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .name {
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-style: normal;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="greeting">
        Hey {{ $('Calendly Trigger').item.json.payload.name }},
    </div>

    <div class="main-text">
        Looking forward to our call.
    </div>

    <div class="gift-highlight">
        <p class="gift-text">I want to give you a completely free training on how I scaled my first six-figure business, step by step, and everything I wish I knew when I got started.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="signature">
        Love and automation,<br>
        <span class="name">Jack</span>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

